#: 01834:5
msgid "She jumped to a conclusion about me!"
msgstr "¡Ha acabado conmigo!"

#: 01834:6
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yeah, well, I know I'm stupid, but you don't have to tell me directly.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Vale. Ya sé que soy estúpido, pero no me lo digas a la cara...\""

#: 01834:9
# REVISAR. <es>{Natsume}\n"Ya veo... Empiezas a parecerme mono."
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I see. You're starting to look cute, Haruma.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Ajá... Estás empezando a parecerme mono, Haruma.\""

#: 01834:10
msgid "Is it because I'm stupid? It made me feel pitiful when she treated me like a kid."
msgstr "¿Es porque soy estúpido? Me entristezvo un poco cuando me trata como a un niño."

#: 01834:11
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't treat me like a kid in front of everyone else, OK?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No me trates como a un niño delante de todo el mundo.\""

#: 01834:14
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"You don't want to be treated like a kid? Did your parents treat you like a kid?\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"¿No quieres que te traten como a un niño? ¿Tus padres no te trataban como tal?\""

#: 01834:15
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, yeah, back when I WAS a kid. How about your parents...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Bueno, claro. Cuando era un niño. ¿Y tus padres...?\""

#: 01834:16
msgid "I was going to say something, but I remembered how we just had this conversation about Natsume-chan's father."
msgstr "Iba a decir algo, pero he recordado la conversación sobre el padre de Natsume."

#: 01834:17
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Where's your Papa now, then?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Dónde está tu padre ahora mismo?\""

#: 01834:18
# Revisar.
msgid "Where could that damn man be? Leaving his cute daughter all alone on an island like this..."
msgstr "¿Dónde podría estar este tipo? Dejando a su preciosa hija en esta isla..."

#: 01834:19
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"He's on this island.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Está en esta isla.\""

#: 01834:20
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What? You mean he's here on the island?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Qué? ¿Que está en la isla?\""

#: 01834:21
msgid "That was an unexpected answer. That meant there shouldn't be any problems, right?"
msgstr "Esa ha sido una respuesta bastante inesperada. Entonces no debería haber problema alguno."

#: 01834:22
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Then you should be able to see him any time you want, right?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Entonces deberías poder verle en cualquier momento, ¿no?\""

#: 01834:23
msgid "It's a small island and hell, they both live here. Given how often Natsume-chan and I bump into each other it should be easy for those two to see each other."
msgstr "Joder, es que es una isla pequeña, y ambos viven en ella. Deberían poder verse."

#: 01834:26
# Revisar. ¿Podría/querría?
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"He wouldn't see me if I tried to visit.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Pero... Él no querría verme.\""

#: 01834:27
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What? Why? You went to go see him, right?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Qué? ¿Por qué? Ya has ido a verle, ¿no?\""

#: 01834:28
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I did, but he ran away from me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Ya lo hice, pero huyó de mí.\""

#: 01834:29
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Why would he run away? Isn't he your father?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Por qué iba a huir? ¿Acaso no es tu padre?\""

#: 01834:32
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"I don't know. Maybe he just hates me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"No lo sé. Quizá es simplemente que me odia.\""

#: 01834:33
# REVISAR! (especialmenet la parte de "por encima del hombro")
msgid "Natsume-chan started pouting. She wasn't acting like her usual aloof self; she was just an ordinary girl right now."
msgstr "Natsume parece resentida. La Natsume de siempre, mira siempre a las personas por encima del hombro, pero la Natsume que veo ahora es como cualquier chica ordinaria."

#: 01834:36
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Papa hates me. That's why he disappeared from me. That's why he won't see me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Mi padre me odia. Y es por eso por lo que huyó de mí. Y es por eso que no querría verme aunque fuese.\""

#: 01834:37
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That's not true.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Eso no es verdad.\""

#: 01834:38
msgid "I didn't know what kind of problems they had between them, but I had to say that."
msgstr "No sé qué problema tendrían entre sí, pero tenía que decirlo."

#: 01834:41
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"What do you know, Haruma?\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"¿Y tú que sabes de mí? Nada. No sabes nada.\""

#: 01834:42
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Maybe I don't, but he's your only father. There isn't a father on Earth that doesn't care about his own child.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Eso es cierto, pero él es tu único padre. No hay ningún padre en el mundo que no se preocupase por su hija.\""

#: 01834:45
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Then why won't he see me? Why would he leave me?\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"¿Entonces por qué no quería verme? ¿Por qué huyó?\""

#: 01834:46
# Revisar.
msgid "It was like we were regressing through the years because Natsume-chan was acting like a little girl."
msgstr "Era como si estuviésemos viajando al pasado por la forma en la que Natsume actuaba como una niñita."

#: 01834:47
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I wouldn't know that either, but all I can say is that your father loves you.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No puedo saber eso tampoco. Pero todo lo que puedo decirte es que tu padre te quiere.\""

#: 01834:48
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"......that's a lie.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...Eso es mentira.\""

#: 01834:49
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Seriously, I mean it. Let's give your father one last chance. I'll go with you to see him this time.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"En serio. Lo creo de verdad. Ves a ver a tu padre una vez más. Esta vez iré contigo.\""

#: 01834:52
# Otra vez Haruno en vez de Haruma.
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"You're going too, Haruma?\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...¿Tú también vendrías, Haruma?\""

#: 01834:53
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yeah. I'll go with you this time, and I'll make sure he doesn't run away so you can see each other.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Claro. Iré contigo esta vez y me encargaré de que no huya para que puedas verle.\""

#: 01834:57
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 01834:58
msgid "Natsume-chan thought for a moment. I thought that she was scared her father might run away and never look at her again."
msgstr "Natsume se quedó quieta durante un rato. Creo que estaba asustada de que su padre no quisiese verla y volviese a huír de ella."

#: 01834:59
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't worry! Believe in me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡No te preocupes! Confía en mí.\""

#: 01834:62
# Revisar.
msgid ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Um...okay...this time you're going with me to meet my father too, Haruma.\""
msgstr ""
"{Natsume}\n"
"\"Um... Vale. Esta vez tú también irás a conocer a mi padre.\""

#: 01834:63
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Right. Got it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Claro.\""

#: 01834:64
msgid "I don't know what kind of parent this guy is, but if he's some nasty jerk, I'll give him a piece of my mind."
msgstr "No sé qué clase de tipo será el padre de Natsume, pero como sea algún capullo, no me callaré."

#: 01834:65
# Revisar. ¿Qué tiene que ver?
msgid "But, I just can't think this guy is a villain because he's Natsume-chan's beloved father."
msgstr "Pero me resulta difícil de creer que sea un mal tipo, siendo el único padre de Natsume."

#: 01834:66
msgid "I really want to help them."
msgstr "Debo ayudarles."
